;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->)
:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::'''Rossy:''' Geez. The moral decay of this place grows more severe by the day. Mark my words. Belobog is on the brink of collapse!
::'''Rossy:''' Look at this. This is today's edition of the ''Crystal Daily''. Here. Look at the front page headline. Do you see it?
::'''Rossy:''' "Supreme Guardian Bronya to organize survey team for exploration beyond the walls: First explorers on the Snow Plains in 700 years."
::'''Rossy:''' Hey, look how riled up I am... Just glancing at this headline is more than I can take!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Isn't this good news?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024185-->
:::'''Rossy:''' How could you call this good? People your age don't get it, including that new Supreme Guardian Bronya. You have no semblance of empathy! Belobog is finished...
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501024189-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Care to enlighten me?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501024189-->
::'''Rossy:''' Do I need to spell it out for you? The former Guardian has passed away not long ago, and now you've got Bronya jumping at the chance to organize a "survey team beyond the walls..." This clearly reflects her inability to make good policy!
::'''Rossy:''' What is Belobog lacking right now? The awareness that there's nothing but wind and snow beyond our city walls? How wasteful do you have to be to take our limited resources and put them into something so insignificant?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' (His complaints are endless... I better not waste any more time here.)
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->)
:{{DIcon|Exit}} You can stay here and keep lecturing.
::'''Rossy:''' Huh? Wow, it's getting late. My mom wants me home for dinner. See you later!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
